data.name: sqlCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT category.Type, category.Id, difficulty.Id AS Expr1, difficulty.Level, words.Id AS Expr2, words.Name, words.Category_id, words.Difficulty_id FROM category INNER JOIN cateog_difficult ON category.Id = cateog_difficult.Category_id INNER JOIN difficulty ON cateog_difficult.Difficulity_id = difficulty.Id INNER JOIN words ON category.Id = words.Category_id AND difficulty.Id = words.Difficulty_id
